---
---

<section class="section" aria-labelledby="why-title">
  <div class="screen-wrapper">
    <div class="why screen">
      <div class="why__inner">
        <div class="why__intro">
          <div class="why__lead">
            <p class="why__label">Why 2.5kg</p>
            <div class="why__title-wrapper">
              <h2 class="why__title" id="why-title">少量では見えにくい<br/>&quot;ごはんとの相性&quot; を、<br/>2.5kgでしっかり確認。</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="why__desc-wrapper">
              <p class="why__desc">毎日のごはんを切り替えるかは、食いつき・便の様子・続けやすさを確かめてから決めたいもの。これらは数日では見えてきません。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="why__table">
          <div class="why__table-row">
            <div class="why__col-labels">
              <div class="why__cell why__cell--head"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--head">確認できること</div></div>
              <div class="why__cell why__cell--label-1"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--label">初日の食いつき</div></div>
              <div class="why__cell why__cell--label-2"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--label-small">食べ続けてくれるかどうか</div></div>
              <div class="why__cell why__cell--label-3"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--label">便の様子</div></div>
              <div class="why__cell why__cell--label-4"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--label">切り替えやすさ</div></div>
              <div class="why__cell why__cell--label-3"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--label-small">毎日の食事としての使いやすさ</div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="why__col-sample">
              <div class="why__col-sample-inner">
                <div class="why__cell why__cell--sample-head"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--sample-head">少量<br/>サンプル</div></div>
                <div class="why__cell why__cell--sample"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--mark">◯</div></div>
                <div class="why__cell why__cell--sample"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--mark">△</div></div>
                <div class="why__cell why__cell--sample"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--mark">△</div></div>
                <div class="why__cell why__cell--sample"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--mark">×</div></div>
                <div class="why__cell why__cell--sample"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--mark">×</div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="why__col-trial">
              <div class="why__cell why__cell--trial-head"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--trial-head">2.5kg<br/>お試し</div></div>
              <div class="why__cell why__cell--trial"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--mark-on">◯</div></div>
              <div class="why__cell why__cell--trial"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--mark-on">◯</div></div>
              <div class="why__cell why__cell--trial-2"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--mark-on">◯</div></div>
              <div class="why__cell why__cell--trial-2"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--mark-on">◯</div></div>
              <div class="why__cell why__cell--trial-2"><div class="why__cell-text why__cell-text--mark-on">◯</div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="why__banner-wrapper">
          <img class="why__banner-img" src="/mca-phsupport/img/group-94.webp" alt="だから、800円でたっぷり しっかり試せることに意味があります。" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why {
    position: relative;
    width: 440px;
    height: 959px;
    background-color: var(--background-02);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .why__inner {
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 24px;
    position: relative;
    top: 64px;
    left: calc(50% - 175px);
    /* フッター(約120px)分を考慮し上に詰める（topはグローバルで固定のためtransformで調整） */
    transform: translateY(-13px);
  }

  .why__intro {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    width: 350px;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    position: relative;
    flex: 0 0 auto;
  }

  .why__lead {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
    position: relative;
    align-self: stretch;
    width: 100%;
    flex: 0 0 auto;
  }

  .why__label {
    position: relative;
    align-self: stretch;
    margin-top: -1px;
    font-family: var(--font-family);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--orange);
    font-size: var(--font-size-s);
    text-align: center;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    line-height: 22px;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .why__title-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    position: relative;
    align-self: stretch;
    width: 100%;
    flex: 0 0 auto;
  }

  .why__title {
    width: fit-content;
    margin-left: -6px;
    margin-right: -6px;
    position: relative;
    margin-top: -1px;
    font-family: var(--font-family);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--brown-amber);
    font-size: var(--font-size-title-xs);
    text-align: center;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    line-height: 1.35;
  }

  .why__desc-wrapper {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    position: relative;
    align-self: stretch;
    width: 100%;
    flex: 0 0 auto;
  }

  .why__desc {
    position: relative;
    flex: 1;
    margin-top: -1px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    font-size: var(--font-size-s);
    letter-spacing: 0;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-family: var(--font-family);
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Comparison table */
  .why__table {
    position: relative;
    width: 350px;
    height: 331px;
    background-color: var(--surface-pale);
    border-radius: 5px;
  }

  .why__table-row {
    position: relative;
    width: 337px;
    top: 6px;
    left: 7px;
    display: flex;
  }

  .why__col-labels {
    width: 179px;
    height: 318px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .why__cell {
    display: flex;
    position: relative;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 9.16px;
    padding: 12.37px;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .why__cell--head {
    width: 179px;
    height: 66px;
    margin-top: 0;
    background-color: var(--table-head-bg);
  }

  .why__cell--label-1 {
    width: 179px;
    height: 45px;
    margin-top: 5px;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-line);
  }

  .why__cell--label-2 {
    width: 179px;
    height: 46px;
    margin-top: 5px;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-line);
  }

  .why__cell--label-3 {
    width: 179px;
    height: 46px;
    margin-top: 4px;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-line);
  }

  .why__cell--label-4 {
    width: 179px;
    height: 46px;
    margin-top: 5px;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-line);
  }

  .why__cell-text {
    position: relative;
    width: fit-content;
    font-family: var(--font-family);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: normal;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .why__cell-text--head {
    color: var(--text-dark);
    font-size: var(--font-size-m);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .why__cell-text--label {
    color: var(--text-dark);
    font-size: var(--font-size-s);
  }

  .why__cell-text--label-small {
    margin-left: -6.87px;
    margin-right: -6.87px;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
  }

  .why__col-sample {
    width: 71.36px;
    margin-left: 4px;
    display: flex;
  }

  .why__col-sample-inner {
    width: 71.36px;
    height: 318px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4.6px;
  }

  .why__cell--sample-head {
    width: 71.36px;
    height: 65.98px;
    background-color: var(--table-head-bg);
  }

  .why__cell-text--sample-head {
    margin-top: -0.84px;
    margin-left: -6.19px;
    margin-right: -6.19px;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    font-size: var(--font-size-m);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .why__cell--sample {
    margin-left: 0.8px;
    width: 70.58px;
    height: 45.82px;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-line);
  }

  .why__cell-text--mark {
    margin-top: -0.42px;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    font-size: var(--font-size-m);
  }

  .why__col-trial {
    width: 78.82px;
    height: 318px;
    margin-left: 3.6px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4.6px;
  }

  .why__cell--trial-head {
    width: 78.82px;
    height: 65.98px;
    background-color: var(--table-trial-bg);
  }

  .why__cell-text--trial-head {
    margin-left: -0.96px;
    margin-right: -0.96px;
    color: var(--white);
    font-size: var(--font-size-s);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .why__cell--trial {
    width: 78.82px;
    height: 45.82px;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-line);
  }

  .why__cell--trial-2 {
    width: 78.82px;
    height: 45.82px;
    background-color: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-line);
  }

  .why__cell-text--mark-on {
    margin-top: -1.42px;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px var(--orange);
    color: var(--orange);
    font-size: var(--font-size-m);
    border-color: var(--orange);
  }

  /* Price banner — Group 94.png 単一画像に差し替え */
  .why__banner-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 350px;
  }

  .why__banner-img {
    display: block;
    width: 350px;
    height: auto;
  }
</style>
